name: Davis County Health
tweet: To order a free radon test kit or to be put on the waiting list to get your home tested with a continuous radon monitor, call the Davis County Health Department at 801-525-5128.

name: Davis County Health
tweet: Radon is a colorless, odorless gas that can enter your home and increase your risk of lung cancer.    1 in 3 Utah homes have elevated radon levels. The only way to know if you have high radon levels is to get your home tested.
